AI Skill Gap Analyzer & Learning Roadmap Generator

SkillSync is a small project I built to explore how multi-agent AI systems can help with career planning.

The idea came from a simple problem:
When we aim for a new job role, itâ€™s hard to clearly know what skills weâ€™re missing and what to learn next. SkillSync acts like a mini AI career assistant that helps answer those questions.

It analyzes your current skills, compares them with a target role, and generates a step-by-step learning roadmap.

