What SkillSync Does

SkillSync simulates a small team of AI agents working together:

â€¢ One agent understands your current skills
â€¢ One agent studies the job role requirements
â€¢ One agent finds the skill gap
â€¢ One agent creates a learning roadmap

Together, they generate a structured plan to help you move toward your target role.

How It Works (Behind the Scenes)

The project uses CrewAI, which allows multiple AI agents to collaborate and complete tasks step by step.

Each agent has a specific responsibility:

Skill Analyst
Takes your current skills and organizes them into structured categories.

Job Analyst
Understands the requirements of the role you want.

Gap Detector
Compares both and finds whatâ€™s missing.

Roadmap Generator
Creates a prioritized learning path based on the gaps.

This workflow shows how multi-agent AI can solve real-world problems.

